
#########################################
####  COMPILING & RUNNING THE CODE   ####
#########################################

1. Complile the source files using make. Run make as follow,
    
     $ make all

2. Running the code with a input files.Also Specify num of Mapper, Reducer & Summarizer threads as arguments.
        
         $  ./wordStatistics <input_file_name>  <num_of_Mappers>  <num_of_Reducers>  <num_of_Summarizers>
   
   Eg:
         $  ./wordStatistics input.txt 3 2 1

   This program genereates wordCount.txt with the word counts & letterCount.txt with the letter count.

